{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Those that were communists and those that believed in the communist ideology-- and we had them, some, in our own family-- almost felt that salvation is at hand.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the Jewish community started to be divided-- those that had sympathies for the communist side, those that had sympathies for the orthodox side.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people were somewhat confused.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it wasn't very long until things really started to change and we began to see just how dangerous our situation was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember in particular when a segment of our Ukrainian neighbors, or the people that lived amongst we lived, started believing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they started to organize themselves to support the side of the fascists in hope of attaining an independent Ukrainian state for themselves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, of course, by embracing that, they declared, again, the Jewish people as their enemies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because all the fascists declared the Jewish people as their enemies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember a day when a public announcer went around and shouted out that on a certain date for 24 hours there is to be no Jewish man, woman, or child on the street.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because their safety is not going to be protected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a certain date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, at a certain date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it-- the Ukrainian people called a congress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On a certain day-- I don't remember what the date was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on that day for 24 hours, there is to be no Jewish man, woman, or child in the streets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have to be in their homes, because they don't guarantee their safety.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the day came, and the big congress was on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the big celebration was on, of course, for the Ukrainians that embraced the fascist ideology.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
